{"article_id":"tkNInuqwU91eDTWr","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"( CNN )","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"President Donald Trump 's allies are mounting a stiff defense of his declaration of a national emergency","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"amid increasing signs","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"that the biggest threat to his border wall now comes not from Congress , but the courts .","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"One of the President 's top policy advisers , Stephen Miller , on Sunday indicated","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"that Trump would cast the first veto of his presidency","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"to defend the highly contentious declaration","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"if lawmakers seek to terminate it .","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"Democrats argued","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"that Trump had launched an unconstitutional power grab","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"because Congress refused to grant his request for billions of dollars in wall funding ,","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"and he decided to fund it anyway with money","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"appropriated for other purposes","depth":11},{"id":13,"text":"including military construction projects .","depth":11},{"id":14,"text":"And California 's Attorney General Xavier Becerra promised to `` definitely and imminently '' launch a legal challenge to the emergency declaration , one of an expected flurry of suits against Trump 's aggressive executive power move .","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"Trump 's announcement ,","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"made during a rambling news conference Friday ,","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"came after he admitted defeat in his bid","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"to get Congress to pay $ 5.7 billion in wall funding ,","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"but avoided triggering a second government shutdown .","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"During that event , the President appeared to undermine his own arguments in several ways","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"by saying","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"he `` did n't need '' to declare the emergency","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"but wanted to go faster than Congress on border security .","depth":11},{"id":24,"text":"Miller tried to clean up that remark in an appearance on `` Fox News Sunday . '' `` What the President was saying is , is that unlike past presidents , he could choose to ignore this crisis ,","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"choose to ignore this emergency","depth":12},{"id":26,"text":"as others have ,","depth":12},{"id":27,"text":"but that 's not what he 's going to do , ''","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"Miller said .","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"The senior adviser , one of the most hardline voices on immigration in the White House , also made clear","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"that","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"if Democratic House Speaker Nancy Pelosi initiates an effort","depth":12},{"id":32,"text":"to wipe out the declaration ,","depth":13},{"id":33,"text":"using a clause in the National Emergencies Act of 1976 ,","depth":13},{"id":34,"text":"Trump would respond .","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"`` He 's going to protect his national emergency declaration ,","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"guaranteed , ''","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"Miller said .","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"Once the House acts ,","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"Senate Majority leader Mitch McConnell is unlikely to be able to prevent a termination effort from coming to the floor ,","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"and","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"given skepticism among some Republicans ,","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"it 's possible a majority could be assembled against Trump 's gambit even in the Senate .","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"Republican Rep. Will Hurd ,","depth":12},{"id":44,"text":"who represents a vast district along the southern border in Texas ,","depth":12},{"id":45,"text":"said","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"he would back a measure in the House","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"that prevents Trump taking money away from military construction projects for the wall .","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"`` I 'm always open to making sure","depth":12},{"id":49,"text":"that Congress takes back some of this power as a co-equal branch of government .","depth":12},{"id":50,"text":"And I 'm sure","depth":12},{"id":51,"text":"there 's going to be a lot of conversations , ''","depth":12},{"id":52,"text":"Hurd said Sunday on `` Face the Nation '' on CBS .","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"But one of the President 's closest congressional allies , Rep. Jim Jordan of Ohio , predicted","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"that Trump 's critics would not be able to put together a two-thirds majority in each chamber of Congress","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"to override any presidential veto .","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"`` I think","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"there are plenty of votes in the House","depth":13},{"id":58,"text":"to make sure","depth":14},{"id":59,"text":"that there is no override of the President 's veto .","depth":14},{"id":60,"text":"So it 's going to be settled in court , ''","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"Jordan said Sunday on ABC News `` This Week . ''","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"Republican Sen. Ron Johnson expressed concern about Trump 's claim of authority","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"to act on the wall","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"- which","depth":12},{"id":65,"text":"some of his colleagues have warned","depth":12},{"id":66,"text":"could establish a precedent for a future Democratic president","depth":12},{"id":67,"text":"to take aggressive executive action on an issue like climate change or gun control .","depth":12},{"id":68,"text":"`` I wish","depth":12},{"id":69,"text":"he would n't use it in this case , ''","depth":12},{"id":70,"text":"Johnson told NBC 's `` Meet the Press '' Sunday","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"and warned","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"that a `` diminished '' Congress had ceded power to the presidency and the courts .","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"But the Wisconsin senator also appeared to offer himself an out from voting against Trump 's assertion of power ,","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"suggesting","depth":12},{"id":75,"text":"there is a good chance","depth":13},{"id":76,"text":"that the GOP will ,","depth":15},{"id":77,"text":"as is often the case ,","depth":15},{"id":78,"text":"decline to constrain its president .","depth":14},{"id":79,"text":"`` We 're going to take a very careful look at what he 's doing here in this instance , ''","depth":12},{"id":80,"text":"Johnson said .","depth":12},{"id":81,"text":"`` But , again , I have to stress","depth":12},{"id":82,"text":"this president 's been thwarted in his attempt","depth":14},{"id":83,"text":"to keep this nation safe and secure .","depth":15},{"id":84,"text":"To secure our borders . `` Let 's face it ,","depth":15},{"id":85,"text":"if this president can claim a mandate on anything","depth":15},{"id":86,"text":"he ran on ,","depth":15},{"id":87,"text":"it 's exactly this issue :","depth":15},{"id":88,"text":"better barriers and securing our border . ''","depth":15},{"id":89,"text":"While polls show","depth":11},{"id":90,"text":"a majority of Americans oppose the wall","depth":12},{"id":91,"text":"and do n't support a declaration of national emergency","depth":13},{"id":92,"text":"to fund it ,","depth":13},{"id":93,"text":"a CNN/SSRS survey","depth":13},{"id":94,"text":"released this month","depth":13},{"id":95,"text":"showed","depth":12},{"id":96,"text":"that 64 % of Republicans do support a national emergency","depth":13},{"id":97,"text":"to get a wall","depth":13},{"id":98,"text":"and 72 % of conservative GOPers back it .","depth":12},{"id":99,"text":"Democrats sought to portray Trump 's action as a gross abuse of power ,","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"arguing","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"that it differs from emergency declarations by previous presidents","depth":12},{"id":102,"text":"and could reshape the relationship between the executive and Congress .","depth":12},{"id":103,"text":"`` This is the first time","depth":13},{"id":104,"text":"a President has tried to declare an emergency","depth":13},{"id":105,"text":"when Congress explicitly rejected funding for the particular project","depth":13},{"id":106,"text":"that the president is advocating , ''","depth":13},{"id":107,"text":"House Democratic Intelligence Committee Chairman Adam Schiff said on CNN 's `` State of the Union '' Sunday .","depth":11},{"id":108,"text":"`` If we surrender the power of the purse ,","depth":14},{"id":109,"text":"which is our most important power ,","depth":14},{"id":110,"text":"there will be little check and no balance left .","depth":13},{"id":111,"text":"It will not be a separation of powers anymore , just a separation of parties .","depth":12},{"id":112,"text":"So this is going to be a moment of truth for my GOP colleagues . ''","depth":11},{"id":113,"text":"Another Democrat , Hawaii Sen. Brian Schatz , resorted to humor","depth":10},{"id":114,"text":"to mock Trump 's use of executive power .","depth":10},{"id":115,"text":"`` Day 3 of Emergency .","depth":13},{"id":116,"text":"Checking in from Oahu .","depth":13},{"id":117,"text":"Light rain , 66 degrees .","depth":13},{"id":118,"text":"Be careful out there , ''","depth":13},{"id":119,"text":"Schatz wrote on Twitter on Sunday .","depth":11},{"id":120,"text":"Day 3 of Emergency .","depth":13},{"id":121,"text":"Checking in from Oahu .","depth":13},{"id":122,"text":"Light rain , 66 degrees .","depth":13},{"id":123,"text":"Be careful out there .","depth":13},{"id":124,"text":"- Brian Schatz","depth":13},{"id":125,"text":"( @ brianschatz )","depth":13},{"id":126,"text":"February 17 , 2019","depth":12},{"id":127,"text":"On a more serious note , Becerra said","depth":7},{"id":128,"text":"that the California court challenge would use Trump 's own remarks","depth":8},{"id":129,"text":"to undermine his declaration","depth":8},{"id":130,"text":"and would argue","depth":7},{"id":131,"text":"that he has created an artificial emergency","depth":8},{"id":132,"text":"that does not meet historic standards of such declarations .","depth":8},{"id":133,"text":"`` We are prepared ,","depth":8},{"id":134,"text":"we knew","depth":10},{"id":135,"text":"something like this might happen .","depth":10},{"id":136,"text":"And with our sister state partners , we are ready to go , ''","depth":9},{"id":137,"text":"said Becerra on ABC 's `` This Week . ''","depth":7},{"id":138,"text":"`` There is enough evidence","depth":9},{"id":139,"text":"to show","depth":9},{"id":140,"text":"that this is not the 9/11 crisis","depth":11},{"id":141,"text":"that we faced back in 2001 ,","depth":11},{"id":142,"text":"it 's not the Iran hostage crisis","depth":11},{"id":143,"text":"we faced in 1979 , ''","depth":11},{"id":144,"text":"Becerra said .","depth":9},{"id":145,"text":"`` It 's not even the type of national emergency","depth":8},{"id":146,"text":"where we are trying to take action against a foreign enemy","depth":9},{"id":147,"text":"or to avoid some type of harm","depth":10},{"id":148,"text":"befalling Americans abroad . ''","depth":10},{"id":149,"text":"Trump is unrepentant .","depth":4},{"id":150,"text":"An emergency declaration in many ways is a neat political device","depth":6},{"id":151,"text":"that allows him to move on from his defeats in Congress over the wall .","depth":6},{"id":152,"text":"Even if his declaration is blocked by the courts ,","depth":6},{"id":153,"text":"it will give him a crusade","depth":7},{"id":154,"text":"with which he can rally his base in his 2020 re-election fight .","depth":7},{"id":155,"text":"In a sing-song refrain , Trump said Friday","depth":6},{"id":156,"text":"that he believed","depth":8},{"id":157,"text":"his effort would be quickly rejected in court","depth":8},{"id":158,"text":"but seemed to pin his hopes on an eventual favorable ruling in the Supreme Court with its new conservative majority .","depth":7},{"id":159,"text":"Until then , Trump is insisting ,","depth":7},{"id":160,"text":"without evidence ,","depth":7},{"id":161,"text":"that he is getting on with fulfilling the campaign promise","depth":7},{"id":162,"text":"that lit a fire under his 2016 campaign -","depth":8},{"id":163,"text":"and which","depth":9},{"id":164,"text":"he seems to be betting","depth":10},{"id":165,"text":"could deliver him a second term .","depth":10},{"id":166,"text":"`` BUILDING THE WALL ! ''","depth":5},{"id":167,"text":"the President tweeted out of the blue on Saturday during his long weekend at his private Florida resort .","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":335,"left":0,"right":334,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":334,"left":315,"right":333,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":315,"left":181,"right":314,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":181,"left":170,"right":180,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":170,"left":1,"right":169,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":169,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":180,"left":173,"right":179,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":173,"left":4,"right":172,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":172,"left":171,"right":7,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":171,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":179,"left":178,"right":14,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":178,"left":8,"right":177,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":177,"left":9,"right":176,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":176,"left":10,"right":175,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":175,"left":11,"right":174,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":174,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":314,"left":292,"right":313,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":292,"left":203,"right":291,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":203,"left":185,"right":202,"relation":"elabora